ected. In this paper, we will use the known\nstopping powers of ions in materials and reaction cross-sections to examine\nthis effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2022 01:04:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-14"}
