e band gap. Our approach is also applicable to a broader range of\ntime-reversal-invariant synthetic materials that do not allow for tailored\nconnectivity, e.g. with nanoscale geometries, and in which synthetic fluxes are\nessential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2022 08:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
