ides\na detailed analysis of the data generation and describes how the data was\ncollected during normal operation of the electricity grid. In addition, we\npresent common anomalies, effects, and trends that could be observed in the PLC\ndata at daily, weekly, or seasonal levels. Finally, we discuss potential use\ncases and the remote inspection of a cable section is highlighted as an\nexample.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2022 12:37:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 14:10:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-13"}
